{"tid":2020911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日第二日，原來真係好難受","createTime":"2020-05-17T11:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T17:40:20.000Z","uid":119446,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fffd3d9d44961504929cde73a8eafaf6e783d1ae","tid":2020911,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:51:36.000Z","msg":"成人個無晒動力，咩都唔想做<br />\n食野都無味，無胃口<br />\n覺得好辛苦好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n當初大家都係真心中意大家<br />\n相處又夾<br />\n以為可以行到最後<br />\n點知會搞成咁<br />\n原來一段幾真摯既感情都會有變質既一日<br />\n<br />\n今日我搵你<br />\n你既口吻就好似第三者咁<br />\n好冷靜，可能你已經放低左<br />\n<br />\n尋日難受，今日都好難受<br />\n訓又訓唔到，做咩都無心情<br />\n一具行屍走肉咁<br />\n合埋眼又諗起我同你既各種回憶<br />\n個心那住那住<br />\n原來生不如死就係咁既感覺<br />\n<br />\n我會覺得好可惜，好遺憾，好無力，好痛苦<br />\n因為我愛過，到而家都係"},{"pid":"56634163a9ff4eae295032abac60351725d89ccb","tid":2020911,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"拍咗好耐？"},{"pid":"81bbece811477bfbc62a5802079c80c0554b0e32","tid":2020911,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"姑姑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0ab18df4f3c91308296998d06e3a99e9900cbf","tid":2020911,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"打完喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40adf293ba1aaaa4cdd0d4f195f8a23282a9cf5","tid":2020911,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56634163a9ff4eae295032abac60351725d89ccb","tid":2020911,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"拍咗好耐？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"差唔多兩年<br />\n係我初戀"},{"pid":"f4b0ce0446fd78c81e091320b8be1c35222a8c2f","tid":2020911,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"女人係咁"},{"pid":"a6371c309c30c8c0acb15cb6223c298f5ee19c65","tid":2020911,"uid":44209